Sarah Liengu Etonge (amụrụ na Buea, Southwest Province, Cameroon) bụ ónyé na-agba ọsọ
O meriri n'asọmpi Mount Cameroon Race of Hope ugboro asaa n'ọbọdọ ya bụ Buea, na Southwest Province
Mmeri kachasị ọhụrụ ya bịara na 2005, na ógè nke 5:38:06. Na Machị 12, 2005, Prọfesọ Emeritus Lydia Luma nke Cameroon Education Corporation nyere Etonge nzèrè doctorate na ugwu
N'afọ 2006, obodo Buea kpughere  oyiyi iji sọpụrụ ya
Ọ bụ naanị  oyiyi nke abụọ e wuru na Buea, na nke mbụ kemgbe ahụ màkà Otto von Bismarck
